snippet.title: Deceit 2 Gameplay Trailer - Future Games Show Summer Showcase 2023
snippet.description:
https://www.youtube.com/@FutureGamesShow

A trailer featuring alpha gameplay of Deceit 2 appeared during this year’s Future Games Show Summer Showcase. Built from the ground up in Unreal Engine 5, this stunning social subterfuge game has a beta you can check out right now by heading to Deceit.GG. Deceit 2 is coming to PC, PlayStation and Xbox in 2023.

#FutureGamesShow #FGS
